title: Selena Gomez and The Weeknd Go on Aquarium Date in Canada: Pics!
text: Selena Gomez and The Weeknd Go on Aquarium Date in Canada: Pics! by Rachel McRady 1:55 AM PDT, March 20, 2017 Photo: Getty Images Taking their love under the sea! Selena Gomez and The Weeknd continued their romantic Toronto, Canada trip on Sunday, visiting the Ripley’s Aquarium of Canada together. A post shared by Selena Gomez Updates (@gomezupdates) on Mar 19, 2017 at 6:36pm PDT A post shared by Selena Gomez Updates (@gomezupdates) on Mar 19, 2017 at 6:36pm PDT In a Boomerang, “The Heart Wants What It Wants” singer spins inside of a plastic orb. For her nautical date, Gomez rocked a white crop top, black pants, and a beige trench coat. The Weeknd also shared a shot of himself looking up at the colorful jellyfish. A post shared by Selena Gomez Updates (@gomezupdates) on Mar 19, 2017 at 6:36pm PDT Last week the pair enjoyed a private movie date after buying all of the tickets to a local screening of the popular horror flick Get Out .
